{"article_id":"8IE0CAJXYI5g9vi8","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Story highlights","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"At least two investigations will be conducted into his death","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"Prosecutor :","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"Castro could n't take","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"what he dished out for a decade","depth":5},{"id":5,"text":"He was sentenced to life in prison plus 1,000 years for a heinous crime ,","depth":6},{"id":6,"text":"but in the end he cut that life short .","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"Ariel Castro ,","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"convicted of kidnapping and raping three women , as well as murder ,","depth":10},{"id":9,"text":"committed suicide in his prison cell Tuesday night ,","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"the Franklin County , Ohio , coroner 's office said .","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"The discovery of the three women","depth":9},{"id":12,"text":"who had been Castro 's captives in his Cleveland home for about a decade","depth":9},{"id":13,"text":"was shocking from the outset , and surprising in its end .","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"Castro , 52 , hanged himself with a bedsheet ,","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"Coroner Dr. Jan Gorniak told CNN on Wednesday .","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"He was being held at the Correctional Reception Center in Orient .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"Castro was taken to The Ohio State University Wexner Medical Center ,","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"where he was pronounced dead at 10:52 p.m .","depth":9},{"id":19,"text":"The Cuyahoga County prosecutor had tough words in the wake of Castro 's suicide .","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"`` These degenerate molesters are cowards , ''","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"Timothy J. McGinty said .","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"`` ... This man could n't take , for even a month , a small portion","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"of what he had dished out for more than a decade . ''","depth":8},{"id":24,"text":"Castro 's brother-in-law , Juan Alicea , told CNN","depth":7},{"id":25,"text":"that the family was notified by the warden about 1 a.m .","depth":7},{"id":26,"text":"The family is angry ,","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"he said ,","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"that it first learned about the death from media reports .","depth":7},{"id":29,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"Why did Ariel Castro kill himself ?","depth":8},{"id":31,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":9},{"id":32,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":9},{"id":33,"text":"Why did Ariel Castro kill himself ?","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"03:09","depth":8},{"id":35,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":9},{"id":36,"text":"Cousin :","depth":15},{"id":37,"text":"'Maybe this is for the best '","depth":15},{"id":38,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":14},{"id":39,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":13},{"id":40,"text":"Cousin :","depth":13},{"id":41,"text":"'Maybe this is for the best '","depth":13},{"id":42,"text":"06:46","depth":11},{"id":43,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"Reporter :","depth":9},{"id":45,"text":"Castro was n't on suicide watch","depth":9},{"id":46,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":8},{"id":47,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":8},{"id":48,"text":"Reporter :","depth":9},{"id":49,"text":"Castro was n't on suicide watch","depth":9},{"id":50,"text":"02:24","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"Alicea said","depth":11},{"id":52,"text":"that Castro 's mother and sister visited him twice in prison , most recently on August 26 .","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"During that last visit ,","depth":14},{"id":54,"text":"both women said","depth":14},{"id":55,"text":"they were worried by his demeanor , mood and body language ;","depth":13},{"id":56,"text":"he appeared depressed ,","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"Alicea said .","depth":11},{"id":58,"text":"But nothing indicated that Castro was contemplating suicide ,","depth":12},{"id":59,"text":"Alicea said ,","depth":12},{"id":60,"text":"recounting what the women told him .","depth":11},{"id":61,"text":"In fact ,","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"he said ,","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"the final letter","depth":13},{"id":64,"text":"that Castro 's mother received from the inmate","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"was more upbeat .","depth":12},{"id":66,"text":"Another family member , Maria Castro-Montes , said","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"she cried","depth":11},{"id":68,"text":"when she heard the news .","depth":11},{"id":69,"text":"Her first thoughts were with the three victims","depth":11},{"id":70,"text":"-- Michelle Knight , Georgina DeJesus and Amanda Berry --","depth":11},{"id":71,"text":"and what they must be feeling .","depth":11},{"id":72,"text":"Would they be glad or angry about Castro 's death ?","depth":11},{"id":73,"text":"The three women","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"held captive by Castro","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"are aware of his suicide ,","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"Knight 's attorney , Kathryn Joseph , told CNN .","depth":9},{"id":77,"text":"She said","depth":9},{"id":78,"text":"the women will not be making a statement .","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"Castro-Montes said","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"nearly everyone in the family had cut ties with Castro ,","depth":10},{"id":81,"text":"and relatives hope","depth":11},{"id":82,"text":"that with his death , the tragic story can come to an end .","depth":11},{"id":83,"text":"`` It was just shock","depth":11},{"id":84,"text":"and part of it was even relief in hopes","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"that now this will just end all of it","depth":13},{"id":86,"text":"and that his name will not be out in the spotlight for years and years to come , ''","depth":13},{"id":87,"text":"she told CNN .","depth":10},{"id":88,"text":"`` I just hope","depth":10},{"id":89,"text":"the victims can move past this now . ''","depth":10},{"id":90,"text":"Castro was not a part of the general prison population ,","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"officials said .","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"`` He was housed in protective custody","depth":11},{"id":93,"text":"which means","depth":12},{"id":94,"text":"he was in a cell by himself","depth":13},{"id":95,"text":"and rounds are required every 30 minutes at staggered intervals , ''","depth":13},{"id":96,"text":"JoEllen Smith of the corrections department told CNN in a written statement .","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"`` A thorough review of this incident is under way , ''","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"she added .","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"At least two investigations will be done ,","depth":11},{"id":100,"text":"according to another corrections department statement .","depth":11},{"id":101,"text":"The prison director commissioned a review team ,","depth":12},{"id":102,"text":"to be made up of legal , medical , mental health , security and operational professionals","depth":13},{"id":103,"text":"not directly involved in the incident ,","depth":13},{"id":104,"text":"to analyze Castro 's death .","depth":11},{"id":105,"text":"The Ohio State Highway Patrol will conduct a separate , independent investigation .","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"But Castro attorney Craig Weintraub said","depth":9},{"id":107,"text":"more precautions against a possible suicide should have been taken .","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"Castro 's attorneys had requested permission for an independent forensic psychologist","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"to evaluate their client ,","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"but were denied by officials ,","depth":11},{"id":111,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"If Castro was believed to be suicidal ,","depth":11},{"id":113,"text":"he should have been under stricter protection ,","depth":11},{"id":114,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":115,"text":"Some will see his death as `` a happy ending to this story , and a quick ending and justifiable , ''","depth":9},{"id":116,"text":"Weintraub said .","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"`` But we 're in a civilized society","depth":9},{"id":118,"text":"and no one should really be celebrating this . ''","depth":9},{"id":119,"text":"In handing down a sentence last month ,","depth":7},{"id":120,"text":"Judge Michael Russo told the kidnapper","depth":8},{"id":121,"text":"there was no place in the world for his brand of criminal .","depth":8},{"id":122,"text":"Castro pleaded guilty to 937 counts ,","depth":10},{"id":123,"text":"including murder and kidnapping ,","depth":10},{"id":124,"text":"in exchange for the death penalty being taken off the table .","depth":9},{"id":125,"text":"The charges stem from his kidnapping , rape and assault of Knight ,","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"abducted in 2002 ;","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"DeJesus ,","depth":13},{"id":128,"text":"abducted in 2004 ;","depth":13},{"id":129,"text":"and Berry ;","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"abducted in 2003 .","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"Castro is the father of Berry 's 6-year-old daughter ,","depth":12},{"id":132,"text":"DNA tests confirmed .","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"`` I cried every night .","depth":16},{"id":134,"text":"I was so alone .","depth":16},{"id":135,"text":"I worried what would happen to me and the other girls every day , ''","depth":15},{"id":136,"text":"Knight , 32 , said ,","depth":14},{"id":137,"text":"as she addressed her abductor head-on during his sentencing .","depth":13},{"id":138,"text":"`` I will live on .","depth":13},{"id":139,"text":"You will die a little every day . ''","depth":13},{"id":140,"text":"In each case , Castro lured the women into his car with the promise of a ride ,","depth":10},{"id":141,"text":"according to court documents .","depth":10},{"id":142,"text":"The women and girl were freed in May","depth":9},{"id":143,"text":"after Berry shouted for help","depth":10},{"id":144,"text":"while Castro was away .","depth":10},{"id":145,"text":"Neighbors heard her cries","depth":11},{"id":146,"text":"and came to her aid","depth":11},{"id":147,"text":"as she tried to break through a door .","depth":10},{"id":148,"text":"One neighbor gave her a cell phone","depth":10},{"id":149,"text":"to call authorities .","depth":10},{"id":150,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":7},{"id":151,"text":"Knight :","depth":8},{"id":152,"text":"'Your hell is just beginning '","depth":8},{"id":153,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":7},{"id":154,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":8},{"id":155,"text":"Knight :","depth":9},{"id":156,"text":"'Your hell is just beginning '","depth":9},{"id":157,"text":"04:07","depth":5},{"id":158,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":6},{"id":159,"text":"Judge paints lonely future for Castro","depth":6},{"id":160,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":7},{"id":161,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":8},{"id":162,"text":"Judge paints lonely future for Castro","depth":8},{"id":163,"text":"01:45","depth":6},{"id":164,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":8},{"id":165,"text":"Cleveland kidnap victims :","depth":9},{"id":166,"text":"Thank you","depth":9},{"id":167,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":8},{"id":168,"text":"MUST WATCH Cleveland kidnap victims :","depth":10},{"id":169,"text":"Thank you","depth":10},{"id":170,"text":"01:50","depth":9},{"id":171,"text":"JUST WATCHED","depth":8},{"id":172,"text":"3 missing women found alive in Ohio","depth":8},{"id":173,"text":"Replay More Videos ...","depth":8},{"id":174,"text":"MUST WATCH","depth":10},{"id":175,"text":"3 missing women found alive in Ohio","depth":10},{"id":176,"text":"02:13","depth":9},{"id":177,"text":"`` Help me ,","depth":7},{"id":178,"text":"I am Amanda Berry , ''","depth":8},{"id":179,"text":"she frantically told a 911 operator .","depth":8},{"id":180,"text":"`` I 've been kidnapped ,","depth":8},{"id":181,"text":"and I 've been missing for 10 years .","depth":8},{"id":182,"text":"And I 'm here ,","depth":8},{"id":183,"text":"I 'm free now . ''","depth":8},{"id":184,"text":"During his sentencing , Castro played the victim ,","depth":7},{"id":185,"text":"saying","depth":8},{"id":186,"text":"he was addicted to porn and masturbation .","depth":8},{"id":187,"text":"In his oft-disjointed statement , he referred to himself as `` very emotional '' and `` a happy person inside . ''","depth":8},{"id":188,"text":"Castro appeared to blame the victims","depth":10},{"id":189,"text":"and accused them of lying about their treatment .","depth":10},{"id":190,"text":"He went on to say","depth":10},{"id":191,"text":"that none of the women was a virgin","depth":12},{"id":192,"text":"when he abducted them ,","depth":12},{"id":193,"text":"that they wanted sex","depth":12},{"id":194,"text":"and there was `` harmony '' in the `` happy household . ''","depth":12},{"id":195,"text":"Castro 's 1,400-square-foot home was reconfigured","depth":12},{"id":196,"text":"to keep their whereabouts a secret ,","depth":12},{"id":197,"text":"FBI agent Andrew Burke testified .","depth":11},{"id":198,"text":"The back door was outfitted with an alarm ,","depth":11},{"id":199,"text":"bedspreads and curtains obscured parts of the home","depth":12},{"id":200,"text":"and a porch swing was placed in front of the stairs","depth":13},{"id":201,"text":"leading to the rooms","depth":14},{"id":202,"text":"where Castro held the women and girl hostage .","depth":14},{"id":203,"text":"Police also testified","depth":11},{"id":204,"text":"Castro would chain the women to objects ,","depth":12},{"id":205,"text":"including a support pole in his basement .","depth":12},{"id":206,"text":"In the room","depth":14},{"id":207,"text":"where Berry and her daughter were held ,","depth":14},{"id":208,"text":"the doorknob was removed ,","depth":13},{"id":209,"text":"a lock was affixed to the outside","depth":13},{"id":210,"text":"and a hole was cut through the door for ventilation","depth":14},{"id":211,"text":"because the windows had been boarded up from the inside ,","depth":14},{"id":212,"text":"Burke said .","depth":11},{"id":213,"text":"Burke also described a handwritten letter","depth":10},{"id":214,"text":"in which Castro claimed","depth":11},{"id":215,"text":"he had been sexually abused as a child","depth":11},{"id":216,"text":"and wrote ,","depth":10},{"id":217,"text":"`` I am a sexual predator . ''","depth":10},{"id":218,"text":"The first police officer on the scene , Barbara Johnson , recalled for the court","depth":9},{"id":219,"text":"how she and another officer heard the pitter-patter of footsteps in a dark room","depth":10},{"id":220,"text":"where Knight and DeJesus were held .","depth":10},{"id":221,"text":"When the captive women realized","depth":11},{"id":222,"text":"they were police ,","depth":11},{"id":223,"text":"Knight `` literally launched herself '' onto an officer ,","depth":12},{"id":224,"text":"`` legs , arms , just choking him .","depth":12},{"id":225,"text":"She just kept repeating ,","depth":12},{"id":226,"text":"'You saved us !","depth":13},{"id":227,"text":"You saved us ! ' ``","depth":13},{"id":228,"text":"Johnson said .","depth":9},{"id":229,"text":"The women were described as scared , pale , malnourished and dehydrated","depth":8},{"id":230,"text":"when they were rescued .","depth":8},{"id":231,"text":"Dr. Gerald Maloney ,","depth":9},{"id":232,"text":"who was in the emergency room","depth":10},{"id":233,"text":"when the victims arrived ,","depth":10},{"id":234,"text":"said","depth":8},{"id":235,"text":"Knight requested","depth":8},{"id":236,"text":"that no male physicians attend to her .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":473,"left":241,"right":472,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":241,"left":0,"right":240,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":240,"left":1,"right":239,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":239,"left":2,"right":238,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":238,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":472,"left":385,"right":471,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":385,"left":264,"right":384,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":264,"left":254,"right":263,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":254,"left":242,"right":253,"relation":"elabora